<TEXT>
the shoreham nuclear power plant is about to 
have its plug pulled without generating a usable kilowatt for long 
island but that didnt stop the nuclear regulatory commission from 
giving an operating license to the controversial reactor 
the commission acted with full knowledge the long island 
lighting co is hoping to rid itself of the 55 billion albatross 
